usage: count_changes.sh [<options>] [-- <git-log-arguments>]

    -h, --help              show this message
    -v, --verbose           print additional info
    -s, --sort-by <field>   sort results based on a field. The valid
                            fields are: total, inserted, deleted, commits and author
    --use-email             use email as part of author string

example:

    $ ./count_changes.sh -s inserted -- next...master
